# 🦐 Aqua Chatbot — AI-Powered Aquaculture Assistant

An intelligent, **bilingual (English & Telugu)** chatbot built to assist shrimp farmers and aquaculture professionals with real-time guidance on water quality, disease detection, feeding, and harvest management.

---

## 🌟 Features

- 💬 **Bilingual Support** — Responds in both English and Telugu
- 🔬 **Disease Identification** — Detects disease-related queries and gives actionable advice
- 💧 **Water Quality Guidance** — Answers questions about pH, oxygen, and ammonia levels
- 🍤 **Feeding Recommendations** — Suggests feeding adjustments based on shrimp growth
- 🌾 **Harvest Guidance** — Advises on optimal harvest timing
- 🤖 **Offline AI Fallback** — Rule-based AI response when specific answers aren't found

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Backend | Python, Flask |
| Frontend | HTML, CSS |
| AI Logic | Rule-based NLP + keyword matching |
| Language Support | English, Telugu |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
aqua-chatbot/
│
├── app.py              # Flask app + AI response logic
├── data.py             # QA knowledge base (bilingual)
├── requirements.txt    # Dependencies
├── static/             # CSS and static assets
└── templates/
    └── index.html      # Chat UI
```

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- pip

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Satya-982/aqua-chatbot.git
cd aqua-chatbot

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run the app
python app.py
```

Open your browser at `http://localhost:5000`

---

## 💡 Use Case

Designed for **rural aquaculture farmers** in Andhra Pradesh and Telangana who need quick, accessible guidance in their native language. Covers common shrimp farming challenges without needing internet-dependent AI APIs.

